Also located on the side is the switch for the illumination of the reticle. This looks much neater and allows quick adjustments in the field. Fast focus eyepieces allow you to adjust the scope to suit your eye strength.
All Targetmaster riflescopes are supplied with a 100mm sunshade and you can choose one of the optional large wheels that suit your needs. Either 100mm or 150mm diameter. Dust Coves are also supplied.
